  "title": "Receptionist cum Coordinator | Northeast | up $2500",
  "description": "<p><strong>HIRING: RECEPTIONIST CUM COORDINATOR</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>LOCATION: NORTHEAST</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>SCHOOL ENVIRONMENT</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>5.5 DAYS WORK WEEK (ALTERNATE SATURDAY)</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>SALARY RANGE: S$2000 - S$2500</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Answers all phone calls politely, and disseminates messages promptly when the staff is unavailable</li><li>Assisting parents in locating their children in school, relay messages to classrooms, sending items from parents to children to the classrooms</li><li>Providing necessary assistance to young primary school children such as contacting parents, sending birthday cakes up to classrooms etc..</li><li>Assists the Directors in making appointments for meeting</li><li>Directs walk-in customers to the Customer Service Executives promptly</li><li>Assists Customer Service Department in ensuring that the brochures are available, updated and accurate</li><li>Arranging dispatch items and coordinates all deliveries/postages</li><li>Ensures a clean and tidy reception area</li><li>Other duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Neat, organized and meticulous</li><li>Passion for children</li><li>Able to work independently</li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates, please send in your resume to: recruit@dismanpower.com.sg & indicate in the subject as \"Receptionist (Northeast)\".</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>DIS Manpower Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 08C3226</p><p>EA Personnel: Sng Wei Lin</p><p>EA Reg No: R1101806</p>",
